♪ The colors blend
in the horizon ♪

00:21:42.036 --> 00:21:45.005
♪ Speeding straight
into a new sun rising ♪

00:21:45.039 --> 00:21:47.508
♪ Never ending seas and
the blue of the sky ♪

00:21:47.541 --> 00:21:49.343
♪ It lies ahead the path

00:21:49.376 --> 00:21:52.046
♪ To what you hope to find

00:22:02.389 --> 00:22:04.692
♪ Well that's right
we'll fly forever ♪

00:22:04.725 --> 00:22:05.859
♪ You know the time to start

00:22:05.893 --> 00:22:07.361
♪ Is now or never

