00:22:40.461 --> 00:22:42.930
[Izzy] The Digimon Encyclopedia!

00:22:42.963 --> 00:22:44.998
HerculesKabuterimon!

00:22:45.032 --> 00:22:48.435
This mega Digimon digivolves
from MegaKabuterimon,

00:22:48.469 --> 00:22:50.104
has a giant horn and pincers,

00:22:50.137 --> 00:22:52.439
and flies around the
world at sonic speed!

00:22:52.473 --> 00:22:54.508
[Tentomon Voiceover]
Now let's check me out!

00:22:54.541 --> 00:22:55.743
[Izzy Voiceover] Hey Tentomon.

00:22:55.776 --> 00:22:57.177
[Tentomon Voiceover]
Despite my tough body,

00:22:57.211 --> 00:22:58.679
my wings are pretty thin,

00:22:58.712 --> 00:23:01.115
but I work them
as hard as I can.

00:23:01.148 --> 00:23:03.617
I can promise you
a safe ride, Izzy!

00:23:03.650 --> 00:23:04.618
[Izzy] Awesome!

00:23:04.651 --> 00:23:06.620
(victorious music)

00:23:09.556 --> 00:23:09.656
Which Digimon will
it be next time?

00:23:11.191 --> 00:23:13.794
[Narrator] With his pride
as the leader on the line,

00:23:13.827 --> 00:23:17.364
Joe challenges the fearsome
Olegmon to a battle.

00:23:17.398 --> 00:23:19.366
[Tai Voiceover] Next time
on "Digimon Adventure:

00:23:19.400 --> 00:23:21.502
Vikemon Ventures the Glaciers."

00:23:21.535 --> 00:23:24.204
[Narrator] The adventure
continues in a new world.

